<h2 local-id=3D"668bb496-642b-45b9-a285-3c5082d3fdd5" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.1CourseCreation">8.1 Course Creation</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2d3f686f-ae37-4320-b037-a4076950d52c"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS a trainer, lead region, head channel, or master user <br>
I NEED to create new courses in the LMS system <br>
SO THAT training programs can be scheduled and managed effectively</p>
<p local-id=3D"fdcbb823-fc51-4f45-b927-7acf4409e293"><strong>Business Use C=
ases:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4f38682e-704a-4cc1-aa2c-473c220dabf3">
<li local-id=3D"38bd67b7-13e7-4964-94d6-ec042dc69f42">
<p local-id=3D"f9b3769e-998c-47b1-b2d3-4f3868ed8e04">Trainer creates SHINE =
course for new agent onboarding</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f2495136-8895-4129-a31d-43190d8a6fea">
<p local-id=3D"c2c66389-529a-4ceb-87c6-0d1c03c44e18">Lead Region schedules =
Product training for existing agents</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8bc919cd-524d-4c0b-a840-6667957c3084">
<p local-id=3D"7aad8190-f833-43cb-92bf-fcf6f3baf37a">Head Channel plans Ski=
ll development courses for their team</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8371c95d-35e8-47c7-b7cb-ecfbf2dd5282" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.1.1CourseCreationForm">8.1.1 Course Creation Form</h3>
<p local-id=3D"dea148a9-3784-424d-a177-8eac1de1223c">The system provides dy=
namic course creation forms that adapt based on the selected course type (S=
HINE, Product, or Skill).</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"3bbe67ca-f18f-4200-bcc5-269150d46a5e" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.1.1.1DynamicFormBehaviorBasedonCourseType">8.1.1.1 Dynami=
c Form Behavior Based on Course Type</h4>
