<li local-id=3D"e9a67fd8-2bea-471f-95da-cdce8db7886a">
<p local-id=3D"2654ecc8-9f08-4958-8d49-bec277565c3c"><strong>Course Type Se=
lection:</strong> User selects from dropdown (SHINE/Product/Skill)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a959018a-864e-4483-8ef9-a0b509b3b0f6">
<p local-id=3D"65efec40-d9d4-4b20-a525-e72f8aa5db48"><strong>Form Template =
Switch:</strong> System loads appropriate field set</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"864505c1-fe97-4597-ba8e-ab1e6481b2c3">
<p local-id=3D"977f21e5-f7e7-4a35-aa2b-700abda1ccdc"><strong>Program List F=
