/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"79703d9f-7a86-4537-9fe9-4f3bbeab7910">
<p local-id=3D"f5f7142f-1312-4c3c-83ec-912acd8fedf0"><strong>Field Visibili=
ty:</strong> MOF and AOL sections show/hide automatically</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdd9eaa4-7bf6-474d-aa42-3054c498eab8">
<p local-id=3D"fde10946-09a1-4c28-abad-9352f4cff2f6"><strong>Validation Rul=
es:</strong> Required fields adjust based on course type</p></li>
</ul>
