<p local-id=3D"bf8dbc89-c4c4-4471-b36e-ed8ec84ff107"><strong>Note:</strong>=
 District field (former Row 31) removed due to Vietnam's administrative ref=
orm effective July 1, 2025. Vietnam transitioned from 3-tier (Province =E2=
=86=92 District =E2=86=92 Ward) to 2-tier (Province =E2=86=92 Ward) adminis=
trative structure.</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"4ec0d4fe-9ce9-4522-a29b-c7d83a82440d" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.1.1.3ProductFormFields">8.1.1.3 Product Form Fields</h4>
<p local-id=3D"0c0f2036-84a4-4f21-81c1-49cb00d50b6b">Product courses use th=
e same base fields as SHINE (rows 1-21 from above) but <strong>exclude all =
MOF-related fields</strong> (rows 22-33).</p>
<p local-id=3D"86fd8a0a-1957-4568-8768-f5ac17fbde6a"><strong>Key Difference=
s:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3faf4551-0d8b-4b42-8a5a-16f7531723b3">
<li local-id=3D"cfab495e-d58d-49d5-9da3-8f7892e621d1">
<p local-id=3D"160328e0-417b-4b55-a1eb-ffd2e0e29a80">No MOF Course Name, Ex=
am Type, MOF Exam Time</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"88ba45f4-267b-45c4-a5e5-ca2a5e2e5836">
<p local-id=3D"31fcbcc5-7a29-4880-ad26-943f1f54a5f3">No Proctor fields</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"d5958694-45cc-42c9-b432-e58537a9005a">
<p local-id=3D"4dc6c7b5-4576-4d5e-98c8-56661c018bc9">No MOF address, Ward, =
Exam categories</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db33fa2e-9d20-41f5-b077-994296ed105b">
<p local-id=3D"2c6c6f67-9107-4809-9572-af30e9d1e781">AOL fields remain opti=
onal</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"65802428-b83d-4f85-b394-533326a4be61" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.1.1.4SkillFormFields">8.1.1.4 Skill Form Fields</h4>
<p local-id=3D"fe1a9c16-83c2-4dd8-a82e-c15fe4064fc9">Skill courses use a mi=
nimal field set:</p>
<p local-id=3D"21cb51cb-74e0-4a14-8f43-d646d52bc957"><strong>Included Field=
s:</strong> Rows 1-17, 21 from SHINE form (basic course information)</p>
<p local-id=3D"779d0b28-cd0f-4629-badb-5c924a68fc9d"><strong>Excluded Field=
s:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"109879f8-58e6-4e12-b0db-b75801b2aee3">
<li local-id=3D"4a407248-fb1d-499b-a3b2-e9bfceacd095">
<p local-id=3D"0c94ba8f-92b7-4cb7-a75d-52b88107db6a">All MOF-related fields=
 (rows 22-33)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7f0b6b47-e9e0-4e34-8f33-2e84e19d98d2">
<p local-id=3D"1f47c20f-9999-4d8c-82bf-0a8567f09255">All AOL-related fields=
 (rows 18-20)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"fcc700f4-9953-4387-9e41-68650470a40b"><strong>Key Difference=
s:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"6b0d2231-f951-4d0c-9733-a71a86e3139f">
<li local-id=3D"ede6cb7c-c4d3-4927-bad0-cb4c3dafc319">
<p local-id=3D"cdf75857-4cf9-47d2-82c3-1434b86e95d1">Focus on core training=
 logistics only</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c3c4fda3-8f9a-4e2a-bf25-e7b1f02d7e6e">
<p local-id=3D"dd9eae77-5ae4-41dd-9371-a79eed310430">No exam-related fields=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d177123-ee19-4274-ba62-c3d8c1a61b1c">
<p local-id=3D"9fddc14c-3384-44f4-9cf3-d29352aa9242">Simplified form for qu=
ick skill training setup</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"8bf4d1e7-1be5-4faa-8a9f-1db496c29d01" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.1.1.5CourseCodeGenerationLogic">8.1.1.5 Course Code Gener=
ation Logic</h4>
<p local-id=3D"0ec5cd0e-bae8-4274-9262-6cee9e926fba"><strong>Business Rule:=
</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"6dc38a54-57f9-4fd9-9f88-27ab530ad2b8">System automatically g=
enerates unique course codes when a course is created. Course code format: =
<code>[SequenceNumber]-[ProvinceCode][ChannelCode]-[CourseTypeCode]</code><=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"7a74a16e-fdc2-47dd-9397-ac1fcd4e256e"><strong>Component Mapp=
ing:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"ee=
3e3841-53ed-4633-be72-31cc5d1cfe75" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr ac:local-id=3D"346c0023-a345-4a01-8a6c-624f83aa422e">
<th data-local-id=3D"bab3e43f-65ab-4126-92be-e7264688a479" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d5e44307-5a3a-47db-91eb-863a512dc497">Component</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"ef1914e6-66d2-4ec4-8dc3-974586288249" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"438998b9-e6de-4faf-b7a9-dbb793ce722d">Source Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f4d08edf-a019-4d9a-8394-30841d822da5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"464b6c33-30d9-4f2f-8536-14d70f4d8a71">Format</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"569c298c-aa1a-463e-b060-b5ca7352c146" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"eb8582c3-6bf7-4c93-af65-c802667f88ba">Examples</p></th>
</tr>
<tr ac:local-id=3D"86aba2a1-0297-414e-ab30-2951a35e33da">
<td data-local-id=3D"77a84e5b-ce7c-4328-a68b-f0bc87dd0b96" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f626a8b8-15cd-4650-b8c2-f38ec08b0b57">SequenceNumber</p></td=
>
<td data-local-id=3D"38c1dedb-96f3-45b6-853a-a9139bef89cc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9a0ad9ae-2397-4410-970b-ab4f931edf5b">Auto-generated</p></td=
>
<td data-local-id=3D"4e32e382-a087-4466-9dbe-f69ddf890f42" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ebf4623c-b48d-4f3c-9e37-772fb074de24">3-digit (001-999)</p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3ef5a718-f856-4921-ac87-834fae67bbd0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3dea31c8-0c49-48e0-85c2-6555b06c74e9">Sequential number for =
uniqueness</p></td>
</tr>
<tr ac:local-id=3D"b6d2414a-5abc-4e25-84bf-2c5029d605a5">
<td data-local-id=3D"2719e7a4-a895-4364-9486-ffe6e394bc97" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1b825f71-7ba8-4492-9c93-acc502acd1b4">ProvinceCode</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c5136059-497d-4621-89a3-b8436013f961" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6a4909fa-136e-4847-b154-1525f01627aa">Province</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a48d109d-c49b-41ab-bc2e-2f88664e0cde" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9a6cad8e-cf11-4447-a0b2-c30655934e68">2 uppercase chars</p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5ff06ce2-8a5b-4e48-b855-dba5c0b16d09" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1bfed72e-282e-48da-a564-580c4ea949b9">HC (Ho Chi Minh), HN (=
Hanoi), DN (Da Nang)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr ac:local-id=3D"78984f0a-c81c-4316-9e75-667836588942">
<td data-local-id=3D"11d9abee-a74e-4690-9973-b83a360864de" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"17ffab55-412e-4fb1-8fec-d0bf3207ce67">ChannelCode</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4769f1a9-06e9-47a2-811d-d81aa3433d8c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"97c206f3-73d0-48a3-9728-0c44e8102447">Channel</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"908ca06c-c8e5-48de-b81a-38be6c371d97" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"13422676-ba57-4c0c-be82-5ed11dbffacf">2 uppercase chars</p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"904a2aa9-2e2a-4d5c-ac4d-fd8b751e5a11" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bcd449c1-8760-4a27-b902-789189f0e797">BC (Banca), AG (Agency=
), BK (Banker)</p></td>
</tr>
<tr ac:local-id=3D"dbeb429f-453a-413a-b9a0-7b9dbc9f4fc3">
<td data-local-id=3D"a5466992-757e-479a-a25a-6d2ee179ad8f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"36525864-880c-44f0-a1ca-234bb260c1bf">CourseTypeCode</p></td=
>
<td data-local-id=3D"9fb751ca-6d75-4900-abaf-5da032229cfe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"99380d5b-f784-470c-9603-211202bd6c0d">Course Type/Program</p=
></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c6ac070e-e5c4-46da-a2b0-af705915bf34" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ab377159-2c81-4047-903c-ceb720e00648">2 uppercase chars</p><=
/td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9a66b2bf-8f4d-40d6-8fe0-9b8836c35352" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3506cb4d-cca3-414b-ba69-217a26a3f830">SH (SHINE), PR (Produc=
t), SK (Skill)</p></td>
</tr>
