<p local-id=3D"f440355e-b5b3-4d5d-9af4-7607923be81a"><strong>Business Rule =
Validation:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e7efc3b0-024d-4518-a1fb-caff204fd388">
<li local-id=3D"4bfe262b-5336-4a0a-a60c-f346e86dff3a">
<p local-id=3D"4e2221c5-e473-4301-bad7-e95935e6e930"><strong>Trainer Availa=
bility:</strong> Warning if trainer has overlapping course assignments</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"e5a6b15a-36aa-479f-aed5-c108163cbeeb">
<p local-id=3D"4ceea08e-415c-41b6-a48d-406b62b5813b"><strong>Program-Course=
 Type Match:</strong> Program must match selected course type</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a144f9ea-598c-4ff1-904a-f521172b4887">
<p local-id=3D"bbe230b7-40af-464c-a0aa-8e13dfaab28d"><strong>Required Field=
s by Type:</strong> MOF fields required only for SHINE courses</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ed79ec5d-00dc-45f7-b5d9-db514f5062dc"><strong>Error Handling=
:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5649518f-c6b0-4f7f-914f-ffc9af75c9d7">
<li local-id=3D"b265d84e-4511-43e3-802b-17c20a811765">
<p local-id=3D"5d683b16-28d3-4711-8c83-302657c98a8c"><strong>Validation Err=
ors:</strong> Display inline error messages below fields</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8a069d53-c157-4cf7-a366-39b91906233b">
<p local-id=3D"122d09a9-5fd2-4ff6-af24-e5a6bfdbe7cb"><strong>System Errors:=
</strong> Display toast notification with error details</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d447a85a-4e10-4eb7-96c3-4df15b71857c">
<p local-id=3D"4f25135d-9e95-4380-9842-d3cf24d13a2e"><strong>Partial Save:<=
/strong> Not supported - all required fields must be complete</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"84017377-18d1-49e6-9fa1-c242643aa997">
<p local-id=3D"5f00c01c-67a1-4ee2-ae23-e7a906bc34b4"><strong>Cancel Action:=
</strong> Prompt user to confirm if form has unsaved changes</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e858bc45-d13b-4c00-881a-e8c7c37e8bbe">
<h2 local-id=3D"2c13ae29-e235-4fd9-8aa9-1c93995f228c" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.2CourseListingScreen">8.2 Course Listing Screen</h2>
<p local-id=3D"26f69ef3-1db6-446f-8cf8-4a9b53445e6c"><strong>Overview:</str=
ong></p>
<p local-id=3D"481a0e77-bfa2-4b49-b999-e96fa0d4db7e">The Course Listing Scr=
een provides a centralized interface for users to view, search, filter, and=
 manage courses in the LMS system. Access and visibility are controlled by =
role-based authorization, ensuring users only see courses relevant to their=
 responsibilities.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"59349d55-38c6-4a83-a7d7-a25852078e79" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.2.1CourseListView">8.2.1 Course List View</h3>
<p local-id=3D"3a11c582-56e9-4a59-8ba1-d0ebc92085ff"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong></p>
<p local-id=3D"a0e3314d-6984-4d87-88aa-4f7cad11f394"><strong>AS</strong> an=
y user who can login to LMS <br><strong>I NEED</strong> to view the course =
list page with data filtered for my role <br><strong>SO THAT</strong> I can=
 view the list of courses relating to me or my channel/region</p>
<p local-id=3D"3b3b5c77-86e0-44bd-9188-14c322a478d6"><strong>Acceptance Cri=
teria:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"023dbdd4-6a78-4ea8-a001-c4a71aa5c3ac">
<li local-id=3D"3a086c3b-f04d-49d2-8638-2afcb6e51357">
<p local-id=3D"d5c3fcae-4689-405b-89c9-74696b4fbbd6"><strong>Course List Di=
splay:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b88e7d12-278a-48af-bfda-f0e99a473d68">
<li local-id=3D"4a6d48d9-4d18-43cb-9b58-e548d7a40043">
<p local-id=3D"7750e66a-e776-480c-aa07-9d0066c03419">Display courses in tab=
ular format with sortable columns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb8be5be-aacc-4b4c-a038-2fae86ecadb4">
<p local-id=3D"a1086e23-0c3a-458d-b7bc-df46a73ae4ec">Default sort: Created =
At (descending - newest first)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afba9640-a2a0-41ac-be2b-24f8a776cccd">
<p local-id=3D"2bbbf8a9-9107-4b13-bef7-b632eab4716d">Pagination with config=
urable rows per page</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d75b446-1bd5-45e9-a335-e08658b5a3d5">
<p local-id=3D"13a74ee9-ea4d-49ef-b703-fc87642172fc">Loading indicators dur=
ing data fetch</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7845ff34-a096-42a4-b288-81433421164f">
<p local-id=3D"64c07d16-ae2c-4fb0-af7e-a71cccfd21c4">Empty state message wh=
en no courses match filters</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"45c3b1f8-59d7-4b58-b44f-0a72416eb5d7">
<p local-id=3D"4061de05-49bc-4e50-b0f9-37d8106b3864"><strong>Role-Based Aut=
horization:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"8dce95dd-943a-4217-893b-4cdacaa9f680">
<li local-id=3D"4c570f24-6648-4f33-a87f-077e45a8d330">
<p local-id=3D"652aaafe-5f79-4738-ba2b-61eb219018d7">System automatically f=
ilters courses based on user role</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2da86b28-54eb-4f2e-a3d6-81ddc903d27e">
<p local-id=3D"b041db8f-7b54-4d21-bef9-6a8e55d7a19c">Authorization rules ap=
ply without user configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2cb0ad3c-73a1-48f7-8b39-83d29f0a27ef">
<p local-id=3D"f3cd5f95-76a7-4100-8a90-01cbbe192167">See Authorization Matr=
ix below</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"c23bf59a-0a67-4d7f-9fd9-b05c4acc1402">
<p local-id=3D"d6bbd2ec-0a5b-4783-a445-4b65970d61f5"><strong>Course Code Hy=
perlink:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"68f229ef-9918-4c7b-b8b1-71a181e21234">
<li local-id=3D"f6f8e961-df94-4515-b099-aef1adf9c27b">
<p local-id=3D"6bda2666-a289-47ff-a035-8165b6b80c41">Course code is clickab=
le/hyperlinked</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9ab9d2a-eb91-4eca-956b-564eaee4f62d">
<p local-id=3D"2132b23b-bd5f-4271-a830-16b8627879d1">Clicking opens Course =
Details Screen in new tab or same window</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"52357830-9df0-4e4f-811b-49e0067be1b9">
<p local-id=3D"d0febe3a-532b-4cc2-a6a7-08aa8a7ee815">Hover shows tooltip pr=
eview</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"ba500b64-1ce5-47aa-a375-aecd894ba387"><strong>Authorization =
Rule for Viewing Courses:</strong></p>
