</div>
<p local-id=3D"81893ff0-3606-4878-be26-3c1e1a3d7531"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e2458cbf-55d2-4eea-8c28-4d8d7679f31c">
<li local-id=3D"6c4874cb-3a34-4373-9dd7-b96fca2f3ab6">
<p local-id=3D"a73eebed-8d5a-4057-a7f4-6db3e32f8412"><strong>Trainer:</stro=
ng></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ba446411-6c86-4579-aaa1-227377b1e583">
<li local-id=3D"fdcfc0b9-c891-43f2-ab38-5cfefec43902">
<p local-id=3D"3edae3db-6b84-4d42-a931-7818a3b7faef">Can view courses where=
 they are Primary Trainer OR Co-Trainer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"333a0378-b4c1-4770-a996-089133f1a78c">
<p local-id=3D"5f79dcd5-5b47-4ced-9251-f939ee5047a3">Can view courses they =
created (as course creator)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"093b0e45-a06f-428f-875b-e7009a155b9d">
<p local-id=3D"82a8b33a-41c2-48da-8a9a-0f986262dd07">Cannot view other trai=
ners' courses unless assigned</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"1427dd11-664d-46aa-8a71-7f358e8160dc">
<p local-id=3D"5348d548-4155-4ed6-b16d-9f296512e63e"><strong>Lead Region:</=
strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"49b202bf-5972-4a09-a611-714d16201b5a">
<li local-id=3D"b8a54c4c-9dac-4cf1-b743-b1a9765587d5">
<p local-id=3D"240b8cae-979b-4d03-acf5-fbfb0522295d">Can view all courses i=
n their assigned channel AND region combination</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a65e3d7-ff93-4481-ac02-9915a5f31927">
<p local-id=3D"e5bd76b5-309d-41c0-930c-48947e44be26">Can view courses they =
created regardless of channel/region</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e8462132-c93c-4968-bf58-f37935131738">
<p local-id=3D"669d4bcf-ff2c-4b0d-8ed7-63c49dfb7983">Example: Lead for "Age=
ncy + South" sees all Agency courses in South region</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c6d5905-7ff6-46da-892e-8262cf0471ce">
<p local-id=3D"0570d7ef-47fb-4039-b52b-9b1249f7248b"><strong>Head Channel:<=
/strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"083bdecd-7010-4f8a-bc06-7c0ed283d04b">
<li local-id=3D"7f0ea433-9838-4a0e-9846-c437df76bd6e">
<p local-id=3D"011e07d6-6cdc-4590-862b-eccbe5fc02b7">Can view all courses i=
n their assigned channel across all regions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03a1984c-cb57-4123-bd55-59ba88fb57ea">
<p local-id=3D"e1b0dfc7-1438-4afb-89f3-19ae416ff4aa">Can view courses they =
created regardless of channel</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00c1a0cb-f394-421e-9841-c7dc30cf616d">
<p local-id=3D"43da497e-bc85-4f9f-a45d-104f4419896c">Example: Head of Agenc=
y sees all Agency courses (North, South, Central, Nationwide)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"a60277ab-8177-4fff-9460-6a1ec4c6463d">
<p local-id=3D"c354d485-ca7e-4d5e-8c9c-e697ff1eeb26"><strong>Admin, Master =
Role, Root Admin:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9ec032c8-47c4-4592-a52c-e4a62ea8cb7a">
<li local-id=3D"46c65169-dbd5-4a75-9d52-d75cda961a55">
<p local-id=3D"208363ab-b43f-4c28-b4f0-f86c65bfdb47">No restrictions - full=
 visibility to all courses in system</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
