<p local-id=3D"a68fc294-1afc-440d-93d7-0f083df1c8fe"><strong>Filter Impleme=
ntation Details:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e5b6d53b-b764-4cc1-a847-518cdcb884f2">
<li local-id=3D"2335c3e1-1fa5-445c-9b1c-a72116f4569c">
<p local-id=3D"1f35fc71-5f36-4dbc-94c8-e4228366d102"><strong>Channel Filter=
:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3bd4b5e8-0808-449c-9b18-3fad89a6e6aa">
<li local-id=3D"5c2e8006-3add-4841-99d2-11c7394522d8">
<p local-id=3D"9490b067-9878-454b-80ce-7c9a637cbc8a">Default: "All" (no fil=
ter applied)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77226945-1c22-438b-88e9-dcd704163ed1">
<p local-id=3D"c50fb7c0-a800-4236-a7e1-facf02e92f56">Single selection dropd=
own</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"57563c7b-5782-4e08-ab16-238b7737ca4e">
<p local-id=3D"505c4a9e-83ee-4acb-a96a-b9827a3cba68">Updates course list to=
 show only selected channel</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80297dbd-8010-4f7c-8399-2daff67d94ba">
<p local-id=3D"83bf9033-0f5c-463f-b672-172cfd4ce886">Respects user role (e.=
g., Head Channel only sees their channel regardless of filter selection)</p=
></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"6433907b-cb76-4c63-a034-f96db87cd59a">
<p local-id=3D"bdb17891-1bd6-49d2-b50d-78759e845e85"><strong>Region Filter:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4ef4e888-9e1c-48e6-b613-91d8169df3a4">
<li local-id=3D"2045449d-b0a9-4eb2-96ef-54254ae5bcf0">
<p local-id=3D"477ff28b-6aa9-4116-ad4e-71e79b330c3d">Default: "All" (no fil=
ter applied)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"852e205c-7bbd-469b-a814-4fddd329047e">
<p local-id=3D"8dad3e18-a12e-4fdb-b58b-0fc6b6bf59db">Single selection dropd=
own</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7afb48cc-c67f-4da2-9e9d-c02796859307">
<p local-id=3D"ba8bb1a2-5af6-4952-af70-d5614554e5e8">Updates course list to=
 show only selected region</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"57d67c83-601c-4f03-aa4f-3f674c4ae6f9">
<p local-id=3D"47f62a3a-7beb-4f20-9edd-66f096e1fb1e">Respects user role (e.=
g., Lead Region only sees their region regardless of filter selection)</p><=
/li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"242afbe7-c8e6-4cd1-a42d-3ad8dbd96e6a">
<p local-id=3D"95a9172d-c6c3-4c4c-b84c-93b22c2fc6bc"><strong>Status Filter:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f872bbad-c515-4bf8-9eae-31b1085083dc">
<li local-id=3D"513d76c8-df54-45b4-94b6-233c2d95c60f">
<p local-id=3D"dfc1393e-9e7c-440b-8699-07b8c1b5c26a">Default: "All" (no fil=
ter applied)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e5ad5c3-21dd-425b-ba2a-ec6b4128b4aa">
<p local-id=3D"38630410-6dd2-4f43-a66c-ac539d5958ee">Single selection dropd=
own</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ab5536c0-d6ed-40b7-99a9-c8da586f1dbe">
<p local-id=3D"1dc891d5-40d0-4147-9e7d-77b71435d728">Shows all course statu=
ses from system</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3ed2657c-5be5-408e-a9d6-b0d9e9e36f39">
<p local-id=3D"43fa9c4a-ca0e-4639-9038-3ae903143ea2">Color-code dropdown op=
tions matching status badge colors</p></li>
</ul></li>
