</ul></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"1135ad8e-03cb-46fd-b0ae-131304d20861"><strong>Search Functio=
nality:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"bb7a79e5-ae9b-4139-9c15-ff91958a545e"><strong>Search Fields:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"300b488a-6281-4e40-b101-a07ff781dc61">
<li local-id=3D"a53767a8-1e10-4b6d-85b9-94671b1ec53c">
<p local-id=3D"7a2d0caf-55d9-4d10-9e7a-927ea021d737">Course Code (e.g., "00=
1-HCBC-SH")</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"748762d7-aab5-4056-8420-cf1857abc431">
<p local-id=3D"2f43bbe5-c850-4724-b911-c4008704fbea">Course Name (e.g., "SH=
INE")</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"12cafdeb-e948-42fc-98b2-ea278047aad3"><strong>Search Behavio=
r:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"08f9ef6e-f68b-41b5-b2c7-36e316ada4e5">
<li local-id=3D"2e40c402-7e26-4f31-8d59-ad01f360df6f">
<p local-id=3D"4c2b9d65-bbf0-45c4-9e58-cace355e79f1"><strong>Partial Match:=
</strong> Search "HC" returns all courses with "HC" in code or name</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"2de1c0e5-a5c4-43cb-a9cd-9e434b69e537">
<p local-id=3D"9be236f5-fe39-42d5-b052-b16dc7323b4d"><strong>Case Insensiti=
ve:</strong> Search "shine" or "SHINE" returns same results</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99a731b1-1318-4bda-9b99-e113a23b77ea">
<p local-id=3D"be92c498-d6e4-408f-aef0-4349d0fefa9e"><strong>Real-time:</st=
rong> Results update as user types OR on button click (configurable)</p></l=
i>
</ul>
