<h3 local-id=3D"c0b2690c-fb7f-4c82-9381-de7f64a8a39c" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.2.3ExportCourses">8.2.3 Export Courses</h3>
<p local-id=3D"7936ba45-18a3-4fe0-ba7a-0c1f8f1ba09f"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong></p>
<p local-id=3D"e21d4bd9-4ca4-4a58-af23-1572734bdfad"><strong>AS</strong> a =
user who can view the course list <br><strong>I NEED</strong> a function to=
 export courses to Excel <br><strong>SO THAT</strong> I can have the list o=
f courses to view offline or share with others</p>
<p local-id=3D"ea7f0b74-ca9d-4378-815f-b5a025831123"><strong>Acceptance Cri=
teria:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"008bafbe-90c1-4138-a7e1-d8afeaf91515">
<li local-id=3D"925974ca-9569-4642-81d4-2b4e29944a41">
<p local-id=3D"f5acf09d-828d-464f-a65b-261241ce7b35"><strong>Export Button:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"19f016d8-c363-41c3-b7f2-d36dc8872185">
<li local-id=3D"a66e9146-db15-4112-809b-2cc6678cc9eb">
<p local-id=3D"bbe2118c-6bf5-4826-9f1c-d2152e1e8603">"Export Courses" butto=
n visible at top-right of course list</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f5f38c8f-b0f1-4ed5-884a-5ad01be5b543">
<p local-id=3D"e78d1efd-f92d-48c2-979b-15e0651ba4de">Button always enabled =
when courses are visible</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"389925c1-209a-4540-a55b-36ab87a6dfa2">
<p local-id=3D"4321c5d2-221f-441b-bb94-d7a0f213c80b">Loading indicator duri=
ng export generation</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"6fd17114-fc6f-413b-8ded-c12c4ab776dc">
<p local-id=3D"470def84-495b-45bf-aa68-186d4fc940f7"><strong>Export Behavio=
r:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"2b1a3aae-3e60-477f-b8a7-38480100b845">
<li local-id=3D"802984a2-0507-425a-ba90-f939fddc0267">
<p local-id=3D"e8586c99-1215-42ec-9b8b-2856e2b25f21">Exports only courses v=
isible to current user (respects role authorization)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5e5f85ae-3432-46c0-85ab-e5313148c293">
<p local-id=3D"feda7710-2e43-423b-b702-e4642a0f1b53">Exports only courses m=
atching current filters/search</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"df19cb71-d090-4586-bf3d-e022db59a8d8">
<p local-id=3D"8b86b86e-4ca4-4b4f-83be-428ffe7bc701">If no filters applied,=
 exports all authorized courses</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"410d1ddf-c6a2-4cb2-a379-648e504bbd5b">
<p local-id=3D"940e4e86-b4c0-4534-bb19-855b778a457f">File downloads automat=
ically when ready</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"2bf3fc18-99a0-415f-9add-731ae21cb06a">
<p local-id=3D"d9cac12f-206e-4b46-aaa4-c34fe70c6db4"><strong>Export Format:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"92b1a8c2-261d-43f7-8182-9ee4bc7bd94a">
<li local-id=3D"3f77c94c-fffe-4708-9c74-2c584f676c36">
<p local-id=3D"c4de8fb3-bfb6-4a17-b011-de10a02a8771">File format: Excel (.x=
lsx)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"01b000ed-91dc-4e78-bfc6-446dabc19969">
<p local-id=3D"18a3b906-2768-47b0-8382-ffea06bb1290">File name format: <cod=
e>Courses_Export_{DDMMYYYY_HHMMSS}.xlsx</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"82a3be9f-0bc3-478e-8d6a-69f44e949f57">
<p local-id=3D"b6362ea6-ed40-43f1-9225-64ad82b4ea34">Example: <code>Courses=
_Export_15032022_143045.xlsx</code></p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"1493a419-2d8c-458d-910b-8a08e837c5d2">
<p local-id=3D"59e8beca-f29b-4725-9296-978cd363dd17"><strong>Export Content=
:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"bca561ab-c873-4767-b532-b9716f2af20e">
<li local-id=3D"ddf2a67d-7a33-47ef-b22b-6a9010d2c7cc">
<p local-id=3D"73e78615-c4dd-400c-875f-7682bf95cdfb">Includes all columns f=
rom Course Listing Fields (Section 8.2.1)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0f7762c-b0fe-47fa-ac99-c10e714a946d">
<p local-id=3D"23729896-014c-4004-a3fc-6e37c69385ed">Header row with column=
 names</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"14e53139-6573-4231-bd61-a5a6ad7ed227">
<p local-id=3D"a3da2449-dbfd-4800-98c1-48c6d8aef9ca">Data formatted consist=
ently with UI display</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d514371-dbef-47f8-8215-71f05c0e26e6">
<p local-id=3D"a81e3e98-39a5-4d83-870c-ec4919f8c75f">Status column shows st=
atus text (not color)</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"e68e8736-fa9b-4187-acc8-f963b6b378cd"><strong>Export File St=
ructure:</strong></p>
