</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"577ea0f0-aef3-45ce-b5b0-9ad7e2bfa609"><strong>Additional Req=
uirements:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a56c3e60-74e2-4ec0-9766-97427140088c">
<li local-id=3D"febc4a5c-dd96-477b-a0e8-7ed4a7a921d6">
<p local-id=3D"4e7a487e-9dbc-48d6-8089-b3571d51e40d">Excel file includes sh=
eet name: "Courses"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0082702d-a65a-4798-9c01-1e632459f559">
<p local-id=3D"28897904-b34e-4fb5-80a2-1c91fcf0fe7c">First row frozen (head=
er row always visible)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4bf943ac-4f04-4ee2-ad28-231546dcdaaa">
<p local-id=3D"d007da93-3ccb-432d-b9bf-e82bcbf3cdf3">Auto-filter enabled on=
 header row</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e166554-f510-445c-885e-9de7d7a79481">
<p local-id=3D"45ab0512-6c38-48f7-a376-dbb3e0f6fa1e">Column widths auto-adj=
usted for content</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2285c9d7-0c81-4e0a-98df-af9807b37cd0">
<p local-id=3D"21911d56-84c4-46ba-aa84-9cddf81e0ac0">Include export metadat=
a (export date, exported by user) in separate row or footer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5d88c1ec-1687-4d34-b021-abcfc025cf4f"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"955effb9-ca45-4f2b-9ea5-df5672c1ac15">
<li local-id=3D"62bda825-5b40-44bc-8ffe-a34a068bccb7">
<p local-id=3D"d27a2e62-caa2-48e4-8728-5462a49f6cf7"><strong>Authorization:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7ebebaad-ff7c-43f5-b42f-b1d41e19b0b4">
<li local-id=3D"fa0bcd67-ed90-4a1f-881d-d34e32347094">
<p local-id=3D"423c6c30-2da9-4edf-8117-d264375ef188">User can only export c=
ourses they have permission to view</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ec5553e-1398-4885-a090-fa45c7aa7751">
<p local-id=3D"ad439ecf-ef92-4c35-b1a7-61c25387e7a9">Export respects same a=
uthorization rules as Course List View (Section 8.2.1)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"268f57f0-95f8-4cac-8395-c310c524663a">
<p local-id=3D"f3e1f93f-5fc0-4941-9fcf-5212e9f9bd82"><strong>Data Integrity=
:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed8ff7ba-2a4f-4b3f-9982-eb3498f8c6ac">
<li local-id=3D"4edc7fcb-2db2-4a77-8c97-439f46702c90">
<p local-id=3D"6f292f3d-a1e1-4034-86bb-6730a5f4d577">Export captures data a=
t moment of export</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"68149a1f-7bba-4d59-baf4-cf4ee35c9a5a">
<p local-id=3D"f5608341-d7b3-4260-b7a4-2eef886399d2">If course is updated a=
fter export, exported file is not updated</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aa2f627d-c3e3-4c53-af3c-5ea7e9ec3f87">
<p local-id=3D"7edacf0d-05b4-41bc-92e8-c4925990270b">Export includes audit =
trail (who exported, when)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"236d4d64-0305-4cdf-9414-5a90a3d57591">
<p local-id=3D"2fc83141-f064-4125-9a69-d29a001fa432"><strong>Performance:</=
strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0776d05e-9670-4a4a-bc5e-5e724f0716ec">
<li local-id=3D"ca58daf6-efde-4303-85ef-d36e32d0c1a4">
<p local-id=3D"363a4aa1-9a37-4a0f-b2c0-542d223da482">Large exports (&gt;100=
0 courses) may require background processing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0a4da8e0-c05a-415c-8324-e2701b6ab8e5">
<p local-id=3D"d6855de0-5b44-4432-83dc-2f00e334d59a">Display progress indic=
ator for large exports</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b98981ec-fca3-473f-a549-c6e500e1a0b0">
<p local-id=3D"07301131-26b0-4e93-9ba1-3d995e60c500">Provide notification w=
hen export is ready (if background processing)</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"35a7cbb4-332c-4eda-a6b3-14c68095f67e">
<h2 local-id=3D"87650a66-bfe1-4558-b06a-0e21eff12ff2" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.3CourseDetailsScreen">8.3 Course Details Screen</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a7ecfd1c-eb34-48dc-91af-e1ccc326efe7"><strong>Overview:</str=
ong><br>
The Course Details screen provides a comprehensive view of all course infor=
mation, status progression, and management capabilities. It serves as the c=
entral hub for viewing and managing individual courses throughout their lif=
ecycle.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9f9db39d-dc9a-41d0-8d93-af5541bd7e39"><strong>Access Points:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"15056a8d-ab12-444c-9741-4566b326aff8">
<li local-id=3D"65323937-bd6b-4cc3-a08a-47f87a8d3103">
<p local-id=3D"9227062a-be7a-4d3b-b691-25d2950de3a3">Click on course code h=
yperlink in Course List</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff37291f-fac1-422c-86fc-360dffd33d82">
<p local-id=3D"ab7b9549-9898-4efe-91d9-fa2fbedd257f">Navigate from Master C=
alendar or PIC Calendar</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d97eed5f-786a-4da7-a38c-9da0daa924d5">
<p local-id=3D"2d7e2da2-8b1f-4f0e-8c3c-2a7349f622a0">Direct URL: <code>/cou=
rses/[courseId]</code></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"623719af-ad78-4275-8c1f-dab9b7636445"><strong>Authorization:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4cb1821e-12a2-4dff-82d5-3efe77a9fcd1">
<li local-id=3D"5ea21b9a-6fc2-4a97-a678-d0a6713ec31a">
<p local-id=3D"080ece01-de5b-4628-be68-2213af0d9082">All users can view cou=
rses based on their role and region/channel permissions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"848d7904-27c2-4081-b077-aa819fc753eb">
<p local-id=3D"8f077d1e-2f59-40b4-a22c-96814c12213d">Edit/Delete/Cancel act=
ions follow role-based authorization matrix (see Section 8.5)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e654c15b-6749-415d-8b1f-70e474a803c1"><strong>Page Structure=
:</strong><br>
The Course Details page consists of:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"9ef4abcb-783e-4b2b-ae27-892d0da98f44">
<li local-id=3D"704d6a6d-8526-4df1-a2d7-1fd794a039bb">
<p local-id=3D"809a3eb3-c6e8-4e6d-a48a-5ca2f8c164c5">Header section with co=
urse title and action buttons</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ca80acb-aa89-4f47-ae14-3cda141fc68d">
<p local-id=3D"52a9c06d-d3e8-4ca9-9ff0-c841c4f0e9a4">Tab navigation (Genera=
l, Planning, Participants, Checklist, History)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94c3c82e-dc2d-456a-aebc-677bc61ca68f">
<p local-id=3D"d1847e99-c816-4777-9f8f-33e3a84cd971">Content area displayin=
g tab-specific information</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"6065a419-0424-443b-962f-c12b53e7a8bc" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.3.1CourseGeneralTab">8.3.1 Course General Tab</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8af7d635-c476-441d-90d3-cab931f09ffa"><strong>Purpose:</stro=
ng><br>
Display all course information fields collected during course creation, org=
anized in an easy-to-read format with status tracking and quick access to m=
anagement actions.</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"056100d8-c8f5-4e3c-b4be-cfaa720b1eaf" id=3D"CourseCreation,=
Listing,Details-8.3.1.1CourseInformationDisplay">8.3.1.1 Course Information=
 Display</h4>
<p local-id=3D"5f90905d-58cd-4c53-8825-203c5f28aca3"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong><br>
AS a user viewing course details<br>
I NEED to see all course information collected during course creation<br>
SO THAT I can review and verify the complete course configuration</p>
<p local-id=3D"32836f20-66da-4ba1-8d78-c213178763e9"><strong>Information So=
urce:</strong><br>
All course information fields displayed in Course Details are the <strong>s=
ame fields collected during Course Creation</strong>. Refer to Section 8.1.=
1 for complete field definitions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"33b2fedf-59d2-4124-8008-c948a0c3c5e6">
<li local-id=3D"77a2bc56-478a-4ce4-af6a-bd5b29ae7e54">
<p local-id=3D"7fb3bc27-4565-4389-bc38-4fa9e1a7045a"><strong>SHINE Course F=
ields:</strong> See Section 8.1.1.2 (Rows 1-33)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4a44dfdd-7e2f-42fc-8b18-2b88f14840d8">
<p local-id=3D"83655aa2-42f8-4013-a362-f502a5995896"><strong>Product Course=
 Fields:</strong> See Section 8.1.1.3 (Rows 1-21, excluding MOF fields)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"5b04755b-f202-4bf4-9abf-d3f3641c0cc2">
<p local-id=3D"2e0016d5-ac71-4ab8-b089-f2f31b32fc18"><strong>Skill Course F=
ields:</strong> See Section 8.1.1.4 (Rows 1-17, 21, excluding AOL and MOF f=
ields)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d576cbf3-d63e-4667-b6ff-b27ea8bab26e"><strong>Note:</strong>=
 District field (former Row 31 in Section 8.1.1.2) removed due to Vietnam a=
dministrative reform (July 2025).</p>
<p local-id=3D"efc0f5a1-0c4c-44da-bd05-7816a3de4c24"><strong>Display Rules:=
</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"df1e8482-2fb8-4796-9c25-86b203e37a07">
<li local-id=3D"ef41323b-0a2c-429b-928f-0f491ffb7b89">
<p local-id=3D"e1180bc9-b895-4543-ba39-6fc2186baf3e"><strong>Field Visibili=
ty:</strong> All fields must be displayed, including empty optional fields<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"18dfb53c-7f5b-4789-829a-7a656799cdfa">
<p local-id=3D"ee478ec8-9d54-4387-973c-dd85cbcffe75"><strong>Empty Field Di=
splay:</strong> Empty fields show "-" or "N/A" as placeholder text</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"52fd3d2f-2886-4f1c-a0a1-2474e51b100b">
<p local-id=3D"0ef93c63-9c51-4cf5-9409-ecadd75e50fe"><strong>Conditional Fi=
elds:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5140c29e-ff57-4cb9-860e-4724dfee1ebd">
<li local-id=3D"afbd24f6-7a43-48b5-9f91-ec21de025583">
<p local-id=3D"08adeabe-b846-4f1e-9e9d-91e0be0b1c5c">AOL fields: Display fo=
r SHINE and Product courses only</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"942d56b3-809e-4610-b2a7-38b04d63d001">
<p local-id=3D"8f64377b-4797-4fb8-817c-52dad8a5525c">MOF fields: Display fo=
r SHINE courses only</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"101e91fb-c6db-4b20-8067-1d5fb77efe9c">
<p local-id=3D"cd9894b2-8b20-420e-81c0-e786c4dc86af"><strong>Read-Only Mode=
:</strong> All fields are read-only in view mode</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"835ca0e7-011b-43bb-8cb0-cd2f897570a2"><strong>Display Mode D=
ifferences:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
